cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "GR_python: Symbolic General Relativity Calculator and Report Generator"
abstract: >-
  Symbolic General Relativity calculator and report generator powered by SymPy
  and LaTeX. The project supports local script-based workflows and a Colab
  notebook workflow for computing curvature tensors, invariants, orthonormal-frame
  quantities, energy conditions, geodesics, and report outputs from user-defined metrics.
type: software
license: "BSD-3-Clause"
